{"tid":1337164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔理多人定少人，全部人同我快撚D出黎，帶埋First Aid物資","createTime":"2019-07-21T08:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T12:18:49.000Z","uid":270504,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"788d82a8b4ac38791b5b64c598c59739d07c3182","tid":1337164,"uid":270504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T08:12:44.000Z","msg":"From 612 reminder:<br />\n1435，一手，遊樂場俾狗查，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">FA物資全被掃</span></span>。<br />\n抄晒ID，CID影晒每一個人嘅樣。<br />\n<br />\n仲未出發既手足請幫手帶<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">First Aid物資</span></span><br />\n物資站手足亦要小心唔好俾狗靠近<br />\n<br />\n物資站地點：<br />\n1.軒尼詩道遊樂場<br />\n2.海富中心<br />\n3.灣仔A4出口、回收膠樽站<br />\n（3. 物資太多，只收水、退熱貼）<br />\n4.太和街遊樂場<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n水站：<br />\n1.恒生灣仔大廈<br />\n2.灣仔298恒大<br />\n3. Sogo 7/f升降機位<br />\n-<br />\n急救站：<br />\n1. St. John：灣仔B1<br />\n2.18區FA站：修頓球場路口"},{"pid":"477253524a8db526da89243e1300e42fe7ca4b12","tid":1337164,"uid":270504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T08:14:36.000Z","msg":"【慎防大包圍 金鐘逃走路線2.0】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1333454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1333454</a>"},{"pid":"d7b5a318166df832d1b7672620a6ca665e58f435","tid":1337164,"uid":270504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T08:15:16.000Z","msg":"出黎啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcbd8b955dc42e6946ce2ba7073e08457d7f478e","tid":1337164,"uid":270504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T08:15:47.000Z","msg":"【慎防大包圍 金鐘逃走路線2.0】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1333454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1333454</a>"},{"pid":"be37eb0977b190fd2faed4d832b8fb2884b2ed51","tid":1337164